        <h2>UNLOCK FREE<br><span>EXPEDITED SHIPPING</span></h2>
        <p class="kngdm-sub">Enter your details below to claim your offer</p>
        <input type="email" id="kngdm-email" placeholder="ENTER YOUR EMAIL ADDRESS" autocomplete="email" />
        <div id="kngdm-phone-wrap">
          <select id="kngdm-flag">
            <option value="+1">🇺🇸 +1</option>
            <option value="+44">🇬🇧 +44</option>
            <option value="+61">🇦🇺 +61</option>
            <option value="+1">🇨🇦 +1</option>
          </select>
          <input type="tel" id="kngdm-phone" placeholder="PHONE NUMBER" autocomplete="tel" />
        </div>
        <button id="kngdm-submit" onclick="kngdmSubmit()">UNLOCK OFFER</button>
        <span class="kngdm-skip" onclick="kngdmClose()">NO THANKS, I PREFER STANDARD SHIPPING</span>
        <p class="kngdm-legal">By submitting this form, you consent to receive informational and/or marketing texts from KNGDM Supply including texts sent by autodialer. Consent is not a condition of purchase. Msg &amp; data rates may apply. Msg frequency varies. Unsubscribe at any time by replying STOP.</p>
